Deemos finished his time in the CR Tank and jumped out, flipping through the
air and landing on his feet perfectly. Shokaract was standing right there in
front of him.

Deemos: I think my people need me.

Shokaract: No, nobody needs you, you're an idiot.

Deemos: I'm also one half of the leader of the Mafia.

Shokaract: You act like you're the only leader, making all of the orders
like you are.

Deemos: I have no idea what you're talking about.

Shokaract: Sure you don't...
